data.value: SELECT COB.*,SUM(TOTAL) OVER() AS TOTALES FROM ( SELECT C.VEND_CLAVE, (SELECT NOMBRE || ' ' || NOMBRE2 || ' ' || APELLIDO_PATERNO || ' ' || APELLIDO_MATERNO FROM PERSONAL P WHERE P.VENDEDOR= C.VEND_CLAVE) NOMBRE_VEND, (SELECT P.EDO_CLAVE FROM PERSONAL P WHERE P.VENDEDOR= C.VEND_CLAVE) AS ZONA, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN C.CLAVE LIKE 'MOS%' THEN COB.TOTAL END),0) AS TOTAL_RESUMEN, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN C.CLAVE NOT LIKE 'MOS%' THEN COB.TOTAL END),0) AS TOTAL_MOSTRADOR, NVL(SUM(COB.TOTAL),0) TOTAL FROM COBROS COB, FORMAS_PAGO FP, CLIENTES C WHERE COB.FOR_PAG_CLAVE = FP.CLAVE AND COB.CLI_CLAVE = C.CLAVE AND TRUNC(COB.FECHA) BETWEEN TO_DATE('07/01/2016','DD/MM/YYYY') AND TO_DATE('06/06/2016','DD/MM/YYYY') AND COB.STATUS_CAN = 'N' AND C.CLAVE IN (SELECT CLI_CLAVE FROM SUC_CLIENTES WHERE SUC_CLAVE=2) GROUP BY C.VEND_CLAVE ORDER BY C.VEND_CLAVE )COB
